data.description: ***ASSUMABLE LOAN AVAILABLE AT 2.99%!  Reach out to listing agent for details*** Rocking chair front porch welcomes you to this lovely 3 bed 2.5 bath with loft on a spacious lot in the quiet neighborhood of Autumn Glen. As you enter the foyer, take note of the low maintenance LVP flooring, 9 ft ceilings and fresh paint throughout. The Formal Dining Room connects the Butler’s pantry featuring granite counters and glass display cabinets convenient to the kitchen. The kitchen is equipped with granite counters, smooth top stove, built-in microwave, dishwasher, disposal, walk-in pantry, island with breakfast bar seating plus stereo speakers in the ceiling. — Just off the kitchen is a breakfast area that leads out to the patio and fenced yard. The patio features a covered pavilion and grilling area for those afternoon BBQs! The large backyard continues beyond the fence and goes down to the creek. — The Great Room boasts great natural light and ceiling fan. Also on the main level is a half bath with pedestal sink. Upstairs is a loft area perfect for another living or entertaining space. The Master bedroom is bright with an attached bath with garden tub and separate shower, tile floors, double vanity, a linen closet, and a his/hers walk-in closet that conveniently opens directly into the Laundry Room for your convenience. There are two additional bedrooms upstairs with walk-in closets and a full bathroom in the hallway with linen closet, oversized vanity and tub/shower. Other features include: 2 car garage and 14x8 shed.  Write your offer today!
